From a young age, she was intrigued by the choices people make, the reason they often put others’ needs before their own and why they fixate on their weaknesses, rather than their strengths. Her passion resulted in a career as a specialist in personal mastery and leadership development. “I love the fact that my work’s authentic to who I am and what I came to this earth to do. I wake up every day knowing that my job has deep resonance with my personality and soul. When you do work that resonates in this way, you’re a better performer and a better learner,” she says. 